{"word":"δέχομαι","slug":"δέχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δέχομαι</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δοχή\">δοχή</a></el>] <b><i>receive</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> with component of enthusiastic acceptance<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of things as objects <b><a href='B:470 11:14'>Mt 11:14</a></b> (instruction); <b><a href='B:480 10:15'>Mk 10:15</a>; <a href='B:490 8:13'>Lk 8:13</a>; <a href='B:490 16:6'>16:6</a></b> <i>(take)<b>;</b> </i><b><a href='B:490 22:17'>22:17</a>; <a href='B:510 7:59'>Ac 7:59</a>; <a href='B:530 2:14'>1 Cor 2:14</a>; <a href='B:540 6:1'>2 Cor 6:1</a>; <a href='B:590 2:13'>1 Th 2:13</a>; <a href='B:660 1:21'>Js 1:21</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of persons as objects, ordinarily in sense of ‘welcome’ <b><a href='B:470 10:14'>Mt 10:14</a>; <a href='B:470 18:5'>18:5</a>; <a href='B:490 2:28'>Lk 2:28</a>; <a href='B:510 3:21'>Ac 3:21</a>; <a href='B:540 11:16'>2 Cor 11:16</a>; <a href='B:550 4:14'>Gal 4:14</a>; <a href='B:650 11:31'>Hb 11:31</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δεύτερος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}